claim.claim-text:
A machine tool comprising:
a column (7) ;
a vertical translation carriage (1) on said column (7);
and
a ram (6), borne by said vertical translation carriage (1) and incorporating a head (10) carrying the working tool and a guide for the transverse movement of the ram (6) with respect to said column (7) ; and
characterized in that on said carriage (1) there is located an operating assembly (11) and at least one perforated plate (2) acting as a bending counter-guide, a fixed sliding block (3), fixed with respect to said carriage (1), and at least one movable sliding block (4, 5), movable with respect to said carriage (1), being arranged on each of said at least one perforated plate (2), which fixed sliding block (3) and at least one movable sliding block (4, 5) are linked with said guide for the transverse movement of the ram (6) with respect to the column (7) of the machine tool, said operating assembly (11) being configured to deform said at least one perforated plate (2) and drag said at least one movable sliding block (4,5), so that the drop of the ram (6) is compensated by means of the controlled bending of the at least one perforated plate (2).
